ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Authorizing to sign, execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers, subject to ratification, the Audiovisual Coproduction Treaty between the Government of Canada and the Cabinet of Ministers of Ukraine
PrecisOrder Authorizing (a) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AUDIOVISUAL COPRODUCTION TREATY BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE CABINET OF MINISTERS OF UKRAINE; or (b) the Minister of Foreign Affairs to execute and issue an Instrument of Full Powers authorizing the individuals mentioned in the order, to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AUDIOVISUAL COPRODUCTION TREATY BETWEEN THE GOVERNMENT OF CANADA AND THE CABINET OF MINISTERS OF UKRAINE.
RegistrationRegistration: UNR/
